text: Marcelle Neveu was a middle-distance runner from France. Neveu competed at the 1928 Summer Olympics. She was born on 2 November 1906 and died on 3 June 1993.Marcelle Neveu == References == Category:1906 births Category:1993 deaths Category:French athletes Category:Middle-distance runners Category:Olympians for France Category:People from Mayenne Category:Sportspeople from Pays de la Loire
